If you prepare yourself, you will be able to get the opportunity for broader experience when it appears.（如果你做好准备，你在面对机会的时候就会有更宽广的经验）
Given that there is a living to be made at night, and given that alternative daytime trades are thoroughly occupied, natural selection has favoured bats that make a go of the night-hunting trade.（考虑到蝙蝠在夜间可以谋生，而且其他白天的交易已经被完全占据，自然选择有利于蝙蝠进行夜间狩猎交易。）
make a go of 做得好，相处得好
